text: Otto Thomsen (June 21, 1884 - October 22, 1926) was an American gymnast. He competed in three events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1884 births Category:1926 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:People from Scott County, Iowa
